title: Bulgogi King Prawn Stir-Fry with Noodles and Sugar Snap Peas
description: Named after Korea's most well-known BBQ dish, bulgogi sauce has a sweet and smoky flavour, thanks to its mix of soy, garlic, brown sugar and pear & apple purees. Bulgogi is a perfect match for rice and noodle dishes or even as a flavour driver in tacos.
